  "texts": [
    "Traditionally, research on TCM case records has depended on manual reading and analysis to extract and summarize diagnostic and therapeutic patterns.",
    "This approach is time-consuming, laborintensive, and fails to comprehensively mine the valuable information contained in the case records.",
    "Consequently, the effective extraction and widespread application of TCM case knowledge have been significantly limited.",
    "Consequently, utilizing contemporary technological approaches to automate the extraction and application of TCM case records has emerged as a primary focus in TCM research.",
    "The rapid advancement of Artificial Intelligence (AI), particularly with the emergence of large language models (LLMs), has created new opportunities for the comprehensive mining and structuring of TCM case knowledge."
  ],
